name: Death
Healing Link
note:
<Custom React Effect>
if (value < 0) {
  var heal = Math.floor(value * 0.5);
  origin.gainHp(-heal);
  origin.startDamagePopup();
  origin.clearResult();
}
</Custom React Effect>

name: Overwatch
note:
<Custom Respond Effect>
if(!user.isActor()){
 var whoCounters = $gameVariables.value(71);
 var whoGetsCountered = $gameTroop.members().indexOf(user);
 var calcSuccess = Math.floor((Math.random() * 100) + 1);
 var successRate = 51;
 if (calcSuccess <= successRate){
  $gameParty.members()[whoCounters].forceAction(1, whoGetsCountered);
  BattleManager.forceAction($gameParty.members()[whoCounters]);
 }
}
</Custom Respond Effect>

name: Death Mark
note:
<Custom Apply Effect>
target._deathMarkDmg = 0;
</Custom Apply Effect>

<Custom React Effect>
if (value > 0 && attacker === origin && this.isHpEffect()) {
  target._deathMarkDmg += value;
}
</Custom React Effect>

<Custom Leave Effect>
target.startAnimation(101);
var dmg = Math.round(-0.50 * target._deathMarkDmg);
target.gainHp(dmg);
target._deathMarkDmg = 0;
target.startDamagePopup();
target.clearResult();
</Custom Leave Effect>

name: Dot Blast
note:
<Custom Regenerate Effect>
if (origin.isAlive()) {
 var dot = $gameVariables.value(150);
 dot = Math.floor(dot);
 target.startAnimation(385);
 target.gainHp(-dot);
 target.startDamagePopup();
 target.clearResult();
 if (target.isDead()) {
  target.performCollapse();
 }
}
</Custom Regenerate Effect>
